Jonathan Taylor Thomas https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Jonathan_Taylor_Thomas 0 Jonathan Taylor Thomas (born Jonathan Taylor Weiss; September 8, 1981) is an American actor, voice actor, and director. He is known for portraying Randy Taylor on Home Improvement and voicing young Simba in Disney's 1994 film The Lion King.
